These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-1::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, train, tram, quad-bike
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: ambient, d&b, funk, techno
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: satire, mystery, comedy, thriller
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: siglo, vegafina, montecristo, oliveros
 1. the fan of ambient is on the right of the fan of d&b##1
 2. the person driving the bike is in an even position##4
 3. the person watching satire movies is on the left of the fan of funk##1
 4. the person watching comedy movies is on the right of the person driving the quad-bike##1
 5. the fan of ambient is on the left or right of the fan of d&b##3
 6. the siglo-smoker is on the left of the person driving the train##1
 7. the person watching mystery movies is the person driving the tram##1
 8. the montecristo-smoker is in an even position##4
 9. the siglo-smoker is between the oliveros-smoker and the fan of techno##2
10. the person driving the bike is the oliveros-smoker##1
11. the fan of funk is the person driving the quad-bike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3      |     4     |
| Transport          | tram  | bike    | quad-bike    | train   |
| Music-Genre   | d&b     | ambient   | funk       | techno    |
| Movie-Genre   | mystery | satire | thriller    | comedy |
| Cigar           | vegafina | oliveros       | siglo | montecristo     |

