.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-2::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: dannemann, oliveros, swisher, fonseca
The people have 4 different hobbies: baking, collecting, drawing, woodworking
The people use 4 different means of transport: scooter, roller, ship, motorbike
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: d&b, ambient, reggae, dubstep
 1. the person who's hobby is woodworking is in an even position##4
 2. the person driving the roller is on the left of the fan of ambient##1
 3. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the right of the swisher-smoker##1
 4. the oliveros-smoker is the person driving the scooter##1
 5. the fan of dubstep is on the right of the dannemann-smoker##1
 6. the person driving the scooter is on the left or right of the person driving the ship##3
 7. the fonseca-smoker is on the right of the swisher-smoker##1
 8. the person driving the motorbike is on the left or right of the fan of d&b##3
 9. the person driving the ship is on the far left or far right##3
10. the swisher-smoker is in an odd position##4
11. the person driving the ship is the person who's hobby is drawing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |    3     |     4      |
| Cigar          | dannemann  | oliveros    | swisher     | fonseca       |
| Hobby         | drawing | woodworking | baking   | collecting |
| Transport   | ship | scooter   | roller   | motorbike    |
| Music-Genre         | reggae | dubstep  | d&b | ambient   |

