.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-3::.
4 different games are played: billiard, backgammon, scrabble, monopoly
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: scientific, documentary, superhero, time-travel
There are 4 different nationalities: british, egyptian, indonesian, italian
House: wooden, craftsman, art-deco, cottage
 1. the person playing billiard is on the left or right of the person watching scientific movies##3
 2. the egyptian is the person watching superhero movies##1
 3. the person playing billiard is on the left or right of the person playing scrabble##3
 4. the person watching scientific movies is on the right of the cottage house##1
 5. the person playing backgammon is the person watching time-travel movies##1
 6. the person playing monopoly is on the left of the craftsman house##1
 7. the wooden house is the italian##1
 8. the person watching time-travel movies is in an even position##4
 9. the person playing scrabble is on the left of the british##1
10. the wooden house is the person playing scrabble##1
11. the person playing billiard is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |     3     |     4      |
| Game      | billiard | scrabble   | monopoly    | backgammon      |
| Movie-Genre           | superhero | scientific | documentary | time-travel     |
| Nationality   | egyptian      | italian   | british   | indonesian |
| House           | cottage         | wooden       | art-deco  | craftsman       |

