.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-4::.
City: liverpool, hamburg, marseilles, london
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: amaryllis, begonia, orchid, bellflower
The people have 4 different hobbies: card-games, chess, sudoku, woodworking
4 different pets are kept: dog, frog, snake, guinea-pig
 1. the person traveling to liverpool is the person who growsamaryllis##1
 2. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the left of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
 3. the person who growsamaryllis is on the left or right of the owner of the snake##3
 4. the person who's hobby is chess is in an even position##4
 5. the person traveling to hamburg is the owner of the guinea-pig##1
 6. the owner of the snake is on the left of the person traveling to liverpool##1
 7. the person traveling to london is on the left of the owner of the snake##1
 8. the person who growsbegonia is on the left or right of the person who growsbellflower##3
 9. the owner of the snake is the person who's hobby is chess##1
10. the owner of the dog is on the left of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
11. the person traveling to marseilles is the person who growsbellflower##1
12. the person who growsbellflower is on the left or right of the person who growsamaryllis##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| City   | london       | marseilles   | liverpool   | hamburg   |
| Flower       | begonia        | bellflower | amaryllis    | orchid       |
| Hobby      | woodworking | chess    | sudoku  | card-games |
| Pet      | frog  | snake  | dog | guinea-pig    |

