The people use 4 different means of transport: motorbike, jet-ski, bike, helicopter
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cricket, ice-hockey, skiing, snowboarding
 1. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the far left or far right##3
 2. the german is between the person who's sport is cricket and the dannemann-smoker##2
 3. the person driving the bike is on the right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
 4. the person driving the jet-ski is the bongani-smoker##1
 5. the person driving the motorbike is on the left or right of the person driving the jet-ski##3
 6. the russian is in an even position##4
 7. the pall-mall-smoker is the person driving the motorbike##1
 8. the german is the person driving the jet-ski##1
 9. the bongani-smoker is on the left or right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##3
10. the person driving the jet-ski is on the right of the thai##1
11. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the left or right of the vegafina-smoker##3
12. the thai is on the left of the person who's sport is skiing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |      2       |       3       |     4     |
