.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-8::.
House: modern, cottage, futuristic, craftsman
The people have 4 different jobs:  social-worker, lawyer, firefighter, paramedic
There 4 different types of food: corn, avocado, plum, pineapple
4 different pets are kept: dog, ferret, horse, turtle
 1. the owner of the turtle is in an odd position##4
 2. the owner of the dog is between the owner of the turtle and the owner of the horse##2
 3. the person eating corn is on the left of the futuristic house##1
 4. the firefighter is in an odd position##4
 5. the person eating pineapple is on the right of the person eating plum##1
 6. the social-worker is on the left or right of the cottage house##3
 7. the owner of the horse is on the left of the futuristic house##1
 8. the cottage house is on the left of the person eating avocado##1
 9. the owner of the dog is between the person eating corn and the lawyer##2
10. the cottage house is on the left of the owner of the dog##1
11. the craftsman house is in an even position##4
12. the social-worker is on the left or right of the modern house##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |    3     |     4     |
| House         | cottage  | futuristic    | modern    | craftsman |
| Job   | firefighter   | social-worker       | lawyer  | paramedic    |
| Food   | corn | avocado | plum | pineapple   |
| Pet           | horse    | dog        | turtle   | ferret    |

