 5. the fan of salsa is between the person watching adventure movies and the person watching animation movies##2
 6. the fan of electronic is in an odd position##4
 7. the person who's sport is cycling is on the right of the person driving the train##1
 8. the person who's sport is handball is on the left or right of the fan of salsa##3
 9. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the left or right of the person who's sport is volleyball##3
10. the fan of techno is on the left or right of the fan of electronic##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |     3      |    4    |
| Transport      | scooter   | boat   | train     | tram   |
| Movie-Genre   | adventure  | spy       | animation | satire |
| Music-Genre           | punk     | salsa   | electronic     | techno     |
| Sport         | volleyball | ice-hockey | handball   | cycling |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-19::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: june, july, december, february
There are 4 different favourite colors: ivory, chestnut, mauve, green
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: game, chaman, alhambra, swisher
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: badminton, sailing, volleyball, water-polo
 1. the person who's sport is sailing is on the left of the chaman-smoker##1
 2. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in july##3
 3. the game-smoker is on the left of the person who's birthday is in february##1
 4. the chaman-smoker is in an even position##4
 5. the person who's sport is badminton is on the right of the person who's birthday is in june##1
 6. the person who likes mauve is on the right of the person who likes green##1
 7. the person who likes chestnut is on the far right##1
 8. the alhambra-smoker is on the far right##1
 9. the chaman-smoker is on the left or right of the person who likes ivory##3
10. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the left of the game-smoker##1
11. the swisher-smoker is in an odd position##4
12. the person who likes ivory is the person who's birthday is in june##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |       2       |     3      |      4      |
| Birthday      | december       | july | june        | february        |
| Color         | green | mauve       | ivory | chestnut |
| Cigar   | swisher     | chaman        | game    | alhambra      |
| Sport         | sailing     | volleyball    | water-polo | badminton   |

