.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-20::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: ambient, house, pop, techno
The people have 4 different jobs:  bartender, analyst, musician, architect
City: berlin, new-york, colone, hannover
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, tea, juice, fanta
 1. the fan of techno is the person traveling to colone##1
 2. the person traveling to colone is between the bartender and the architect##2
 3. the person traveling to colone is on the left or right of the person traveling to berlin##3
 4. the person drinking tea is on the left of the analyst##1
 5. the person traveling to berlin is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1
 6. the fan of house is the person traveling to new-york##1
 7. the person drinking juice is on the left or right of the person drinking tea##3
 8. the architect is in an even position##4
 9. the person traveling to new-york is on the left or right of the person traveling to berlin##3
10. the bartender is in an even position##4
11. the bartender is on the far right##1
12. the fan of ambient is on the right of the musician##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |     3      |     4      |
| Music-Genre   | house      | ambient | techno     | pop        |
| Job   | musician | architect  | analyst     | bartender |
| City         | new-york    | berlin | colone      | hannover |
| Beverage     | fanta | tea     | juice | 7up       |

 